Description:
Pure period grace & a McKinnon Zoned address
Make a premier College Zone address your Mission! Proximity to leading schools, including McKinnon College, makes this period residence so desirable. On 680sqm approx this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom light-filled Spanish Mission home is a rare find in the area. Beyond fine formal rooms, light & spacious family living flows from a timeless timber kitchen to a sun-bathed northerly deck, while a cleverly zoned plan places master-suite (with frameless-screened ensuite & WIR) away from kids' bedrooms in a quiet rear wing. With a secure garage in lush tank-watered surrounds, this gracious residence combines rich period detail (including story-book leadlight windows, elaborate ceilings & fireplaces) with modern comforts ...and one of the area's most family-wise addresses.
4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, (ensuite), WIR
lounge, dining, light-filled family zone, garage
timber kitchen, duct heating, rev-cyc air-con
4,600L water-storage, McKinnon College Zone

Description:
Period grace, easy living space...Zone address
Move right in & enjoy the period grace you love, the easy living space you need & the College Zoning you want!! A walk to the College in compact corner gardens, this substantial solid-brick 3 bedroom period beauty is perfectly appointed with a CaesarStone kitchen (with 900mm prestige Savoir-faire oven), a glossy polished porcelain bathroom, reverse-cycle air-con & ducted heating. Inside, there's pressed glass doors & a fireplace for the traditional lounge, dining beside the kitchen & a relaxed family area with space to lounge, study & step out to paved entertaining. Outside, there's 2-car parking including carport, landscaped gardens ...& Joyce Park & the North Rd bus at either the end of the street! Land 430sqmts approx.

Description:
Secure City Style Apartment/Penthouse Position!
In the heart of Ormond shopping strip, this spacious penthouse style top floor apartment features 2 balconies (a wide terrace off the open plan living and the other off the main bedroom) with lovely tree top views and a clever 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom dual suite plan perfect for share housing.
Fitted with granite kitchen bench tops throughout, stainless steel appliances, BIR's, European laundry, heating and air-con, intercom and 2 basement car parking plus a storage cage, this is a rare penthouse opportunity in the McKinnon college zone.
Perfect for the 1st home buyer, young professionals, those looking for the spaciousness of a house with the security offered by an apartment or make this a brilliant investment in a rarely vacant group.
With Ormond station at your doorstep, North Rd Brighton beach just moments away and Chadstone shopping centre just a short drive away what more could you want.

Stylish renovation, central location
$350,000-$380,000
Move right in, rent right out, secure your future in this fully renovated, wonderfully secure apartment. With undercover parking & intercom entry beyond auto-gates, this 1st-floor apartment makes the most of its quiet rear position with a touch of luxury. Step beyond a glossy front door to find parquet- floored living flowing out to a private balcony, fresh carpets through 2 robe-fitted bedrooms & the comfort of reverse-cycle air-conditioning. Styled up with a sophisticated Blanco appliance kitchen & sleek fully-tiled bathroom with private WC & laundry facilities, this deluxe apartment has style to adore ...with a location owner-occupiers & tenants alike will love near Ormond station & shops.
